article_title: Zenefits Says It Is Laying Off 250 Employees
article_text:
Zenefits is dismissing 250 employees, or roughly 17% of its workforce, in a major retrenchment for a health-benefits-brokerage company that less than a year ago was touted as one of Silicon Valley’s most promising startups.

The cutbacks were concentrated in sales, the company said.
